## PERFORMANCE & INFINITE LOOP AUDIT REPORT

### 2.1 useEffect Dependencies Analysis

**CRITICAL FINDINGS:**

#### App.tsx - Line 48
```typescript
useEffect(() => {
  const loadedHistory = db.getAll();
  setHistory(loadedHistory);
